room_title: Escape room "Wizard Hysteria" by Alcatraz Escape Games in Phoenix
room_address: 1290 N Scottsdale Rd. Suite 103 Tempe, AZ 85281
room_description: In an evil twist of fate, He-Who-Must-Not-Be-Named has once again escaped death and returned to torment the wizarding and Muggle worlds alike. You and your wizarding cohort find yourself trapped within the walls of Hogwarts - with only an hour to spare before the Dark Lord lets loose the Cruciatus Curse on you unlucky lot.
